verses.roman:
śrīmanta, gokula-dāsa hariharānanda
śivāi, nandāi, avadhūta paramānanda

synonyms: śrī-manta—of the name Śrīmanta; gokula-dāsa—of the name Gokula dāsa; hariharānanda—of the name Hariharānanda; śivāi—of the name Śivāi; nandāi—of the name Nandāi; avadhūta paramānanda—of the name Avadhūta Paramānanda.
translation: Śrīmanta was the forty-fifth, Gokula dāsa the forty-sixth, Hariharānanda the forty-seventh, Śivāi the forty-eighth, Nandāi the forty-ninth and Paramānanda the fiftieth.
